channel.description:
This is just an easier way to set your client to run on VPS or localhost IPs. Its pretty easy to implement this fully, as I am only giving you the ternary string and boolean. :P
[code=java]/** * True = connect to local host False = connect to VPS */ public static final boolean LOCALHOST = true;
public static final String VPS_IP = "Your_Vps_IP";
public static final String SERVER = LOCALHOST ? "localhost" : VPS_IP;[/code]
Its simple really, but it saves you some time to live your life a few seconds longer.
